# += after removal or whenever a used mask is inadvertently touched, clean hands with an alcohol-based handrub, or soap and water if hands are visibly dirty;  replace masks as soon as they become damp with a new clean, dry mask; do not re-use single-use masks; discard single-use masks after each use and dispose of them immediately upon removal.
